WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:08.000
What do you think decides faster —
your brain or your consciousness?

2
00:00:09.850 --> 00:00:15.170
One and the same movement can be perceived
as care or as threat,

3
00:00:15.330 --> 00:00:18.800
as liberation or as loss of control.

4
00:00:20.050 --> 00:00:22.150
This is how interference arises.

5
00:00:23.350 --> 00:00:26.300
And then a human being is also a wave.

6
00:00:27.680 --> 00:00:31.900
We will now place neuro-headsets on your heads,

7
00:00:31.900 --> 00:00:34.820
provided by the Neiry company —

8
00:00:34.850 --> 00:00:39.800
they read the brain's wave activity in real time.

9
00:00:39.900 --> 00:00:43.350
The virtual world follows its own rules
and only sometimes synchronises with ours.

10
00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:47.950
Remember the person you could have become —
but didn't.

11
00:00:48.470 --> 00:00:51.600
The scene is ready for playback.

12
00:01:03.750 --> 00:01:07.490
Perhaps reality is not a fixed stage,

13
00:01:07.490 --> 00:01:12.300
but a continuous process of co-creating the world.

14
00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:21.300
Dear viewers, we have completed
the preparation of all five scenes.
